  "title": "DISHWASHER - KITCHEN STEWARD",
  "description": "<p>Position: Dishwasher / Kitchen Steward</p>\n<p>Location: CAFFE BEVIAMO - TANGLIN MALL AND/OR ONE HOLLAND VILLAGE</p>\n<p>Employment Type: Full-time / Part-time</p>\n<h3>Job Summary</h3>\n<p>We are looking for a reliable and hardworking Dishwasher / Kitchen Steward to support our kitchen team. You will be responsible for maintaining cleanliness and hygiene in the kitchen, washing dishes and utensils, and assisting with basic kitchen duties when needed.</p>\n<h3>Key Responsibilities</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Wash and sanitize all dishes, glassware, utensils, and kitchen equipment</li>\n  <li>Keep dishwashing and kitchen areas clean, organized, and free of hazards</li>\n  <li>Remove garbage and clean waste areas regularly</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with food safety and hygiene standards</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>No prior experience required (training will be provided)</li>\n  <li>Willingness to work in a fast-paced environment</li>\n  <li>Good physical stamina; able to stand for long periods</li>\n  <li>Team player with a positive attitude</li>\n  <li>Punctual, responsible, and able to follow instructions</li>\n  <li>Availability to work on weekends and public holidays (as required)</li>\n</ul>",
